  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.title": "MengSama Net Music: Playlist Manual",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.description": "Introduction to MengSama Net Music: Playlist",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list.title": "Playlist",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list.description": "The core of the mod",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list.add_music.title": "Burning",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list.add_music.text1": "Put the playlist item into the CD burner, the mod has been adapted for direct burning. $(br)(If songs are overwritten, see the next chapter)$(br)Use the list/ prefix to burn NetEase playlists.",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list_ui.title": "Interface",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list_ui.text1": "Hold the playlist item and click to open an interface, click the options in the list to select songs. $(br)If 'Add Song' is selected, the burned song will be appended to the playlist, otherwise it will overwrite the current song. $(br)You can switch play modes, delete and move songs in this interface.",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list_use.title": "Usage",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.play_list_use.text1": "Just put it in the music player. (Note: not the vanilla jukebox)",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.title": "Portable Music Player",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.description": "Using MengSama Net Music without a portable player is like using PS only for green screen removal",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.use.title": "Usage",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.use.text1": "Prepare a CD or playlist with content (playlists cannot be in append mode), pick it up in your inventory, and left-click the player to insert it for playback, right-click the player to take out the internal CD/playlist. $(br)When containing an item, the player will display the current song info in the item tooltip.",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.fast_select.title": "Quick Song Select",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.fast_select.text1": "While the portable player is playing music, right-click to open the quick song select menu (on the right side of the screen), use the scroll wheel to select songs, and use it again to switch songs. $(br)Hold the speed-up key (default Left Shift) to accelerate scrolling, hold the translation key (default Left Alt) to show translated song names. $(br2)Red songs are VIP songs and currently cannot be played.",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.hud.title": "Song Info HUD",
  "patchouli.mengsamanetmusic.music_player.hud.text1": "The portable player displays song info in the upper left corner while playing music, including song cover, name, translation, playback progress and lyrics.",
